## Zweck

Codeberg API Token für Repository-Verwaltung.

## Details

| Feld | Wert |
|------|------|
| **Typ** | Codeberg API Token |
| **Token-Name** | codeberg_api.token |
| **Berechtigung** | repository: Lesen und Schreiben |
| **Verschlüsselung** | age (passphrase) |

## Entschlüsselung

```fish
# 1. Derived Key generieren
cd /mr-bytez/shared/deployment
fish derive_key.fish secrets

# 2. Secret entschlüsseln
age -d shared/.secrets/api/codeberg.token.age > /tmp/token
# → Passphrase = Derived Key eingeben

# 3. Token an Zielort kopieren
cp /tmp/token ~/.secrets/api/codeberg_api.token
chmod 600 ~/.secrets/api/codeberg_api.token
rm /tmp/token
```

